nds containing six carbon atoms, such as [[:en:Hexane|hexane]] and {{ill|hexyl group|ja|ヘキシル基|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/hexyl group|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. * The opposite counterpart in the Ten Stems cycle is {{ill|Kō|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kō|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=}}. * The {{ill|lucky direction|ja|恵方|3=歳徳神|1=Toshitoku-shin|lt=Lucky direction|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/lucky direction|13=User:Immanuelle/Toshitoku-shin|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 歳徳神}} (Eho) for Ki is slightly east of northeast (75 degrees). ==Sexagenary cycles containing Tsuchinoto (己)== {{wikt|己}} {| class="wikitable alternance droite" |{{ill|Yin Earth Snake|ja|1=Yin Earth Snake|己巳|zh|1=Yin Earth Snake|己巳|ko|기사|fr|Serpent de terre|de|Erde-Schlange|en|Earth Snake|lt=己巳 (Yin Earth Snake)|lt_ko=기사|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Snake|qq=}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yin Earth Rabbit|ja|1=Yin Earth Rabbit|2=ja|己卯|zh|1=Yin Earth Rabbit|2=ja|己卯|ko|기묘|fr|Lièvre de terre|de|Erde-Hase|en|Earth Rabbit|lt=己卯 (Yin Earth Rabbit)|lt_ko=기묘|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Rabbit|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yin Earth Ox|ja|1=Yin Earth Ox|2=ja|己丑|zh|1=Yin Earth Ox|2=ja|己丑|ko|기축|fr|Buffle de terre|de|Erde-Büffel|en|Earth Ox|lt=己丑 (Yin Earth Ox)|lt_ko=기축|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Ox|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yin Earth Pig|ja|1=Yin Earth Pig|2=ja|己亥|zh|1=Yin Earth Pig|2=ja|己亥|ko|기해|fr|Cochon de terre|de|Erde-Schwein|en|Earth Pig|lt=己亥 (Yin Earth Pig)|lt_ko=기해|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Pig|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yin Earth Rooster|ja|1=Yin Earth Rooster|2=ja|己酉|zh|1=Yin Earth Rooster|2=ja|己酉|ko|기유|fr|Coq de terre|de|Erde-Hahn|en|Earth Rooster|lt=己酉 (Yin Earth Rooster)|lt_ko=기유|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Rooster|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yin Earth Goat|ja|1=Yin Earth Goat|2=ja|己未|zh|1=Yin Earth Goat|2=ja|己未|ko|기미|fr|Chèvre de terre|de|Erde-Schaf|en|Earth Goat|lt=己未 (Yin Earth Goat)|lt_ko=기미|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Goat|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |} == See Also == * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
